OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FThe government has announced further
OL,7,Fsocial media restrictions for
OL,8,Fteenagers as it continues to roll out
OL,9,Fplans aimed at protecting young people
OL,10,Fonline.
OL,12,FA social media curfew and restrictions
OL,13,Fon scrolling are among the new
OL,14,Fmeasures.
OL,16,FSo what are the proposed changes and
OL,17,Fhow could you be affected? ITV News
OL,18,Fexplains.
OL,20,FWhat are the new restrictions?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
