OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784081889
OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FSixteen and 17-year-olds will face an
OL,7,Fovernight social media curfew,
OL,8,Frestrictions on infinite scrolling and
OL,9,Fbreaks in AI chatbot use under new
OL,10,Fgovernment plans.
OL,12,FThe changes, part of the government's
OL,13,Fwider restrictions on social media for
OL,14,Fchildren, will introduce default
OL,15,Fsettings that prevent access for older
OL,16,Fteenagers between midnight and 6am.
OL,18,FFeatures that keep users hooked, such
OL,19,Fas never-ending reels and algorithmic
OL,20,Ffeeds, will automatically be turned
OL,21,Foff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
