FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784081889
OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FAre the restrictions mandatory?
OL,8,FWhile these restrictions will become
OL,9,Fthe default settings, they are
OL,10,Fvoluntary, so you will be able to
OL,11,Fswitch them off on your device.
OL,13,FThis has prompted critics to question
OL,14,Fthe effectiveness of the measures.
OL,16,FWhen do they come into place?
OL,18,FThe proposals will be presented to
OL,19,Fparliament by the end of 2026, with
OL,20,Fthe expectation that they could come
OL,21,Finto force in Spring 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
