OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FHow do these plans fit into wider
OL,7,Fmeasures?
OL,9,FLast month, the government unveiled a
OL,10,Fsocial media ban for under-16s, which
OL,11,Fis expected to cover platforms
OL,12,Fincluding Snapchat, TikTok, YouTube,
OL,13,FInstagram, Facebook and X, but not
OL,14,Fmessaging services like WhatsApp and
OL,15,FSignal, also from next spring.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
