OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FThe announcement came days before the
OL,7,FMakerfield by-election, but it will
OL,8,Ffall to incoming prime minister Andy
OL,9,FBurnham to figure out key details.
OL,11,FWhat is the point of the new rules?
OL,13,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall said
OL,14,Fthe latest measures will help ensure
OL,15,Funder-18s accessing social media apps
OL,16,Ffor the first time won't suddenly be
OL,17,Fexposed to the most addictive features.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
