OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784081889
OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,F"These measures will be crucial in
OL,7,Fhelping young people get the sleep
OL,8,Fthey need, focus on school and
OL,9,Fcollege, and spend more quality time
OL,10,Fwith family and friends, all of which
OL,11,Fare fundamental to building a happy,
OL,12,Fhealthy and fulfilling adult life,"
OL,13,FKendall said.
OL,15,F"We want young people to enjoy the
OL,16,Fbenefits of technology while having
OL,17,Fthe tools to make the online world a
OL,18,Fplace where they can thrive."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
