OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784081889
OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FFamilies who took part in a government
OL,7,Fpilot involving more than 300
OL,8,Fteenagers and parents across the UK
OL,9,Freported that overnight curfews helped
OL,10,Fimprove sleep and concentration,
OL,11,Faccording to the Department for
OL,12,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,13,F(DSIT).
OL,15,FKendall also wants to introduce new
OL,16,Fsafeguards for children using
OL,17,Fartificial intelligence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
