PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784081889
OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FThe proposals include requiring under-
OL,7,F18s to take regular breaks while using
OL,8,Fchatbots and a crackdown on AI
OL,9,Fservices that provide "dangerous,
OL,10,Fmisleading or unverified mental health
OL,11,Fadvice", with ministers considering
OL,12,Fbanning chatbots that pose a serious
OL,13,Fthreat to children, the DSIT said.
OL,15,FNew guidance for children, parents and
OL,16,Fguardians on safe AI use will be
OL,17,Fpublished, and media literacy teaching
OL,18,Fwill be strengthened in schools from
OL,19,FSeptember.
OL,26,@qD@WOUsD@GO]
