OL,3,CHow will the new social media curfew
OL,4,Cfor teenagers work?
OL,6,FHow have the new measures been
OL,7,Freceived?
OL,9,FConservative shadow education
OL,10,Fsecretary Laura Trott described the
OL,11,Fmove as "another dog's dinner" from
OL,12,FLabour.
OL,14,F"Either they think 16 and 17-year-olds
OL,15,Fshould be on social media, or they
OL,16,Fdon't, but curfews they can simply
OL,17,Fswitch off won't achieve anything.
OL,19,F"Giving 16-year-olds the vote while
OL,20,Fputting them under a social media
OL,21,Fcurfew makes no sense."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU
